sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  participant U as SOC Analyst
  participant FE as Operator UI
  participant BE as /api/v1/operator
  participant IP as intent parser (LLM)
  participant SP as safety_policy
  participant AP as approval gate
  participant AX as ansible_exec
  participant SRV as Monitored Server
  U->>FE: natural-language instruction
  FE->>BE: POST prompt (asset_id)
  BE->>IP: parse intent + generate playbook
  IP-->>BE: intent + playbook_yaml + risk_level
  BE->>SP: safety classification (scope, risky ops)
  SP-->>BE: tier + blocked_reasons
  BE-->>FE: preview (explanation, playbook, risk)
  alt low risk and in scope
    U->>FE: confirm
    FE->>AP: approve (admin secret)
    AP->>AX: execute
    AX->>SRV: SSH run
    SRV-->>AX: result
    AX-->>BE: OperatorRun completed
  else risky or out of scope
    BE-->>FE: blocked (requires manual review)
  end
  BE-->>FE: result + audit log
